<?xml version="1.0" encoding="utf-8" standalone="yes"?><rss version="2.0" xmlns:atom="http://www.w3.org/2005/Atom"><channel><title>Metrics on materialize-monitoring Documentation</title><link>https://sturdy-adventure-l4w34ye.pages.github.io/metrics/</link><description>Recent content in Metrics on materialize-monitoring Documentation</description><generator>Hugo</generator><language>en-us</language><atom:link href="https://sturdy-adventure-l4w34ye.pages.github.io/metrics/index.xml" rel="self" type="application/rss+xml"/><item><title>Scraping</title><link>https://sturdy-adventure-l4w34ye.pages.github.io/metrics/scraping/</link><pubDate>Mon, 01 Jan 0001 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://sturdy-adventure-l4w34ye.pages.github.io/metrics/scraping/</guid><description>&lt;h1 id="scraping-metrics-with-materialize-monitoring"&gt;Scraping Metrics with &lt;code&gt;materialize-monitoring&lt;/code&gt;&lt;a class="anchor" href="#scraping-metrics-with-materialize-monitoring"&gt;#&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h1&gt;
&lt;p&gt;By default, &lt;code&gt;materialize-monitoring&lt;/code&gt; is configured to scrape metrics from any ServiceMonitor or PodMonitor resources in the cluster.
This allows you to easily add new metrics to your monitoring stack by simply creating a new ServiceMonitor resources.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h2 id="scrape-architecture-with-grafana-alloy"&gt;Scrape Architecture with Grafana Alloy&lt;a class="anchor" href="#scrape-architecture-with-grafana-alloy"&gt;#&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;code&gt;materialize-monitoring&lt;/code&gt; runs Grafana Alloy with a &lt;code&gt;prometheus.operator&lt;/code&gt; component on &lt;code&gt;alloy-gateway&lt;/code&gt; instances (Deployment) which reads ServiceMonitors and PodMonitors in order to determine what targets to scrape.&lt;/p&gt;</description></item><item><title>Storing</title><link>https://sturdy-adventure-l4w34ye.pages.github.io/metrics/storing/</link><pubDate>Mon, 01 Jan 0001 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://sturdy-adventure-l4w34ye.pages.github.io/metrics/storing/</guid><description>&lt;p&gt;TODO&lt;/p&gt;</description></item><item><title>Querying</title><link>https://sturdy-adventure-l4w34ye.pages.github.io/metrics/querying/</link><pubDate>Mon, 01 Jan 0001 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://sturdy-adventure-l4w34ye.pages.github.io/metrics/querying/</guid><description>&lt;p&gt;TODO&lt;/p&gt;</description></item><item><title>Rules</title><link>https://sturdy-adventure-l4w34ye.pages.github.io/metrics/rules/</link><pubDate>Mon, 01 Jan 0001 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://sturdy-adventure-l4w34ye.pages.github.io/metrics/rules/</guid><description>&lt;h1 id="metric-rules"&gt;Metric Rules&lt;a class="anchor" href="#metric-rules"&gt;#&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h1&gt;</description></item></channel></rss>